definition: Zaozhuang prefecture level city in Shandong
farmstead/village/manor/place of business/banker (in a gambling game)/grave or solemn/holdings of a landlord (in imperial China)

sentences.english: In recent years, karst collapses have frequently occurred in Zaozhuang City.
sentences.chinese: 近年來棗莊市岩溶塌陷頻繁發生。
